Class Summary
AsynchronousAnnotation Simple Asynchronous sample that demonstrate how task can be asynchronously executed.

EventsLogger  
FileResource  
JAXBBean  
JQueryPubSub Simple PubSub resource that demonstrate many functionality supported by Atmosphere JQuery Plugin and Atmosphere Jersey extension.
MeteorPubSub Simple PubSub resource that demonstrate many functionality supported by Atmosphere JQuery Plugin (WebSocket, Comet) and Atmosphere Meteor extension.
PubSub Simple PubSub resource that demonstrate many functionality supported by Atmosphere.
PubSubBroadcaster A example of how to extends/replace Broadcaster by defining the class value in META-INF/atmosphere.xml or by adding defining the org.atmosphere.cpr.broadcasterClass init-param in web.xml.
TypedChannel Simple Resource acting like a channel of communication.
WebSocketPubSub Simple PubSub resource that demonstrate many functionality supported by Atmosphere JQuery Plugin and WebSocketHandler extension.
